name: Tez Dizpenser ⁄ Mercury ⁄ SYSTEMA SOLARIS ⁄ #9
description: Meet Mercury. SYSTEMA SOLARIS is a series of 10 works that captures the sheer beauty and size of our solar system. Each unique 1 of 1 Tez Dizpenser showcases that celestial body's scale, moon(s), rings, color and its distant view of the sun. Join me on this space-bound voyage. Collect them all! 〔 Diameter: 3,032 mi 〕〔 Length of Day: 4,222 hr 〕〔 Distance from Sun: 36 million mi 〕〔 Average Temperature: 333°F 〕〔 Number of Moons: 0 〕 Twitter: @cmilburndesign – Clubhouse: @codestrong
